i-mahi-with-coconut-rice-and-mango-salsa/	/Cuisine/Latin American/Caribbean/	Total Fat 29g 37%, Saturated Fat 18g 91%, Cholesterol 94mg 31%, Sodium 549mg 24%, Total Carbohydrate 107g 39%, Dietary Fiber 4g 14%, Total Sugars 21g, Protein 31g, Vitamin C 21mg 106%, Calcium 81mg 6%, Iron 8mg 43%, Potassium 888mg 19%	Prep Time: 30 mins, Cook Time: 30 mins, Additional Time: 1 hrs, Total Time: 2 hrs, Servings: 4, Yield: 4 servings	https://www.allrecipes.com/thmb/_Br00LE_QdFo9AuCW0UnlID2Cms=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/820135-48af5355baf04fcc96a1af9bd4f92a61.jpg
